---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  lang="en"
  title="Fitness &amp; Strength Training Guides - AIVancePro"
  description="Complete fitness and strength training guides. Learn the basics, create your program and progress effectively."
  canonical="https://aivancepro.fr/en/guides/"
  alternates={{ fr: 'https://aivancepro.fr/guides/', en: 'https://aivancepro.fr/en/guides/', de: 'https://aivancepro.fr/de/ratgeber/' }}
>
  <Fragment slot="head">
    <style>
      .page-header {
        padding: 9rem 2rem 3rem;
        text-align: center;
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--gray-50), var(--white));
      }
      .section-label {
        display: inline-block;
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.08em;
        color: var(--blue);
        margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
      }
      .page-header h1 {
        font-size: 2.8rem;
        font-weight: 800;
        letter-spacing: -0.02em;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
      }
      .page-header p {
        color: var(--gray-500);
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        max-width: 550px;
        margin: 0 auto;
      }
      .guides-grid {
        max-width: 1000px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 3rem 2rem 6rem;
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
        gap: 1.5rem;
      }
      .guide-card {
        background: var(--white);
        border: 1px solid var(--gray-200);
        border-radius: 16px;
        overflow: hidden;
        text-decoration: none;
        color: var(--gray-900);
        transition: border-color 0.2s, transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
      }
      .guide-card:hover {
        border-color: rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.3);
        transform: translateY(-4px);
        box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
      }
      .guide-card .card-image {
        width: 100%;
        height: 180px;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--gray-100), var(--gray-200));
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        color: var(--gray-400);
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        font-weight: 500;
      }
      .guide-card .card-content {
        padding: 1.5rem;
        flex: 1;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
      }
      .guide-card .tag {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 0.2rem 0.6rem;
        background: rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.06);
        border-radius: 50px;
        font-size: 0.7rem;
        color: var(--blue);
        font-weight: 600;
        margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
        width: fit-content;
      }
      .guide-card h2 {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        line-height: 1.35;
      }
      .guide-card p {
        color: var(--gray-500);
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        line-height: 1.6;
        flex: 1;
      }
      .guide-card .meta {
        margin-top: 1rem;
        font-size: 0.75rem;
        color: var(--gray-400);
        font-weight: 500;
      }
      .cta-section {
        padding: 5rem 2rem;
        text-align: center;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--dark), #1a1145);
        color: var(--white);
      }
      .cta-section h2 {
        font-size: 2.2rem;
        font-weight: 800;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
      }
      .cta-section p {
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
        font-size: 1rem;
        max-width: 450px;
        margin: 0 auto 2rem;
      }
      .btn-primary {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 0.5rem;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--blue), var(--purple));
        color: var(--white);
        text-decoration: none;
        font-size: 1rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        padding: 0.875rem 2rem;
        border-radius: 12px;
        transition: opacity 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.3);
      }
      .btn-primary:hover {
        opacity: 0.92;
        transform: translateY(-2px);
      }
      @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .page-header { padding: 7rem 1.5rem 2rem; }
        .page-header h1 { font-size: 2rem; }
        .guides-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      }
    </style>
  </Fragment>

  <header class="page-header">
    <div class="section-label">Guides</div>
    <h1>Complete Guides</h1>
    <p>Detailed guides to master every aspect of your training, from beginner to advanced.</p>
  </header>

  <section class="guides-grid">
    <a href="/en/guides/beginner-strength-training/" class="guide-card">
      <div class="card-image img-placeholder">Beginner Guide Photo</div>
      <div class="card-content">
        <span class="tag">Beginner</span>
        <h2>Beginner's Guide to Strength Training</h2>
        <p>Everything you need to know to start strength training: basic exercises, program structure and mistakes to avoid.</p>
        <div class="meta">15 min read</div>
      </div>
    </a>
    <a href="/en/guides/create-training-program/" class="guide-card">
      <div class="card-image img-placeholder">Program Photo</div>
      <div class="card-content">
        <span class="tag">Programming</span>
        <h2>Creating an Effective Training Program</h2>
        <p>Sets, reps, frequency and volume: the keys to building a program that delivers results.</p>
        <div class="meta">12 min read</div>
      </div>
    </a>
    <a href="/en/guides/nutrition-training/" class="guide-card">
      <div class="card-image img-placeholder">Nutrition Photo</div>
      <div class="card-content">
        <span class="tag">Nutrition</span>
        <h2>Nutrition and Training: The Complete Guide</h2>
        <p>Protein, calories, macros and meal timing. Everything you need to optimize your results through nutrition.</p>
        <div class="meta">18 min read</div>
      </div>
    </a>
    <a href="/en/guides/recovery-injury-prevention/" class="guide-card">
      <div class="card-image img-placeholder">Recovery Photo</div>
      <div class="card-content">
        <span class="tag">Recovery</span>
        <h2>Recovery and Injury Prevention</h2>
        <p>Sleep, stretching, deload and fatigue management. Learn to recover better to progress faster.</p>
        <div class="meta">10 min read</div>
      </div>
    </a>
    <a href="/en/guides/periodization-basics/" class="guide-card">
      <div class="card-image img-placeholder">Periodization Photo</div>
      <div class="card-content">
        <span class="tag">Advanced</span>
        <h2>Periodization Basics</h2>
        <p>Microcycles, mesocycles and macrocycles: structure your long-term training to progress without plateauing.</p>
        <div class="meta">14 min read</div>
      </div>
    </a>
    <a href="/en/guides/improve-bench-press/" class="guide-card">
      <div class="card-image img-placeholder">Bench Press Photo</div>
      <div class="card-content">
        <span class="tag">Strength</span>
        <h2>How to Improve Your Bench Press</h2>
        <p>Technique, programming and accessory exercises to effectively increase your bench press.</p>
        <div class="meta">11 min read</div>
      </div>
    </a>
    <a href="/en/guides/home-gym-guide/" class="guide-card">
      <div class="card-image img-placeholder">Home Gym Photo</div>
      <div class="card-content">
        <span class="tag">Home Gym</span>
        <h2>Home Gym Guide: Training at Home</h2>
        <p>Essential equipment, setup and adapted programs for effective training at home.</p>
        <div class="meta">13 min read</div>
      </div>
    </a>
    <a href="/en/guides/understanding-rpe/" class="guide-card">
      <div class="card-image img-placeholder">RPE Photo</div>
      <div class="card-content">
        <span class="tag">Technique</span>
        <h2>Understanding RPE and Intensity</h2>
        <p>RPE scale, RIR and 1RM percentage: how to dose intensity to optimize every session.</p>
        <div class="meta">9 min read</div>
      </div>
    </a>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-section">
    <h2>Put it into practice</h2>
    <p>Download AIVancePro and let the AI coach apply these principles to your training.</p>
    <a href="https://apps.apple.com/app/aivancepro/id6756116760" class="btn-primary" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Download for free</a>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
